      "notes": "Mechdusa is a Hardmode boss exclusive to worlds that combine the For the Worthy and Remix seeds. Technically, it is not considered a separate boss, but is merely a combination of all three mechanical bosses . It resembles a large serpentine-like creature composed of the three bosses: The Destroyer 's head is attached to Skeletron Prime 's head, and The Twins are individually connected via tendrils to Skeletron Prime's eye sockets instead of to each other. There are also two extra Probes attached to The Destroyer's head."
